            <div type="text">
                <div type="transcription">
<p>I beg leave to call the attention of the C. to the enclosed statement with respect to the Surplus Fund showing a balance against the fund for the closing year of £ 9.12.6. It is illegal to expend money entrusted for sickness for this but as there was a small balance in favour of the Fund last year the deficiency may be passed over.</p>
<p>During the following year if the Committee order the same payments as before the amount paid from the Surplus Fund will be as follows</p>
     
            <table>
                <row>
                    <cell rend="left">Doctor</cell>
                    <cell rend="right">12.</cell>
                    <cell rend="right">12.</cell>
                    <cell rend="right">0</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell rend="left">Clerk</cell> 
                    <cell rend="right">2.</cell>
                    <cell rend="right">19.</cell>
                    <cell rend="right">6</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell rend="left">Rent of Club-Room</cell>
                    <cell rend="right">2.</cell>
                    <cell rend="right">0.</cell>
                    <cell rend="right">0</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell rend="left">Payment to Committee</cell>
                    <cell rend="right" cols="3">.10</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell rend="left">Stationery</cell>
                    <cell rend="right" cols="3"> ? ?</cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell rend="left">(last year the extraordinary sum of 6<hi rend="superscript">s</hi> was paid for <hi rend="italic">[</hi>stationery<hi rend="italic">]</hi></cell>
                    <cell rend="borderBottom" cols="3"/>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell/>  
                    <cell rend="right">£18:</cell>
                    <cell rend="right">1:</cell>
                    <cell rend="right">6</cell>
                </row>
</table>
     
<p>As we have received this year for Honorary Subscriptions &amp; Fines 8.5.6, there will be supposing that we have the same next year a balance against the Surplus Fund of 9.16.0.<ref target="#foot.f2"/> Therefore the Doctor can be paid out of the Surplus Fund only for the first Q, &amp; the members must pay the other 3 remainder. Even then there will be a balance of 7<hi rend="superscript">s</hi> against the Surplus Fund &amp; this must not be repeated another year.</p>
                    <p>I am sorry for this unprecedented state of affairs, but as long as I remain Treasurer, Trustee &amp; Hon. Member, I can do nothing illegal.</p>
<p>Your obed servt. | C. D.  <lb resp="#mjhawkins"/></p>
                    <p rend="left">Dec 31<hi rend="superscript">st</hi> | To the Council of the D. F. Club</p> 
                </div>
            </div>
